{{Noticebox/Community}}
'''Manage VRChat''' refers to the various tools available for managing VRChat friends, worlds, avatars, groups, and other features outside of gameplay. In addition to the VRChat client and the [https://vrchat.com/home VRChat website], third-party applications provide alternative interfaces for interacting with VRChat through the [[VRChat API]]. Third-party tools often extend or improve on features available in VRChat. Where a tool provides a notable quality-of-life enhancement over the built-in implementation, this is noted in the table below.

